text: Andrej Startsev (born 7 June 1994) is a Kazakhstani footballer who plays as a right back for VfB Oldenburg. == Club career == Startsev is a youth exponent from FC St. Pauli. He made his 2. Bundesliga debut 23 September 2014 against Eintracht Braunschweig playing the full game in a 1–0 home win. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Kazakhstani footballers Category:German footballers Category:Living people Category:FC St. Pauli II players Category:FC St. Pauli players Category:Association football defenders Category:2.
